\f1\fs24 GENE ROBERTS

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:03.800
\f2 : The ranch is located not too far from
Durango, Colorado. An area that has generally

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:11.289
been referred to at times as the Switzerland
of the West, and we have lots of tall, tall

00:01:11.289 --> 00:01:18.150
mountains. We have more 14,000-foot tall peaks
within three miles of here than any place

00:01:18.150 --> 00:01:23.930
else in North America, grouped together. The
ranch is at 7800 hundred feet, but it rises

00:01:23.930 --> 00:01:32.090
rapidly. A lot of our rides go quickly to
10,200 feet. Some to 11,000 feet. A variety

00:01:32.090 --> 00:01:34.090
of terrain from low to high. \
