00:01:36.090 --> 00:01:39.409
\f2 : Staying at this ranch in Southern Colorado
allows one to explore the vast wilderness

00:01:39.409 --> 00:01:44.560
by day and hunker down in a warm cabin at
night. This type of guest ranch caters to

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:47.620
families, incorporating special programs for
kids.

