\f1\fs24 JAN ROBERTS

00:01:50.620 --> 00:01:52.659
\f2 : We knew we didn\'92t want to live in
a city for the rest of our lives, so we started

00:01:52.659 --> 00:01:58.009
looking for a ranch and initially we actually
looked for a cattle ranch, but we found that

00:01:58.009 --> 00:02:03.710
it\'92s difficult to make money in the cattle
business. Still is, and it evolved into looking

00:02:03.710 --> 00:02:09.289
for a dude ranch. So we came upon Wilderness
Trails and we negotiated with the owner and

00:02:09.289 --> 00:02:16.049
we bought it in ah. We started negotiating
in 1969. We actually bought it the end of

00:02:16.049 --> 00:02:20.379
\'9269 and moved here in the spring of \'9270.
This is my office. You can\'92t beat that.

